Class ToolOutput

java.lang.Object
  edu.harvard.hul.ois.fits.tools.ToolOutput

public class ToolOutput
extends java.lang.Object

The output created by a Tool. A ToolOutput object holds JDOM objects representing the FITS output and the raw form of the output.
